data.title: 2017 18commencement Program
data.meta_description: 2017 18commencement Program - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides the order of exercises and program for a University of Colorado Boulder commencement ceremony to be held on May 10, 2018 at Folsom Stadium. It includes the processional, national anthem, commencement address by Governor Kate Brown, conferring of awards including Chancellor's Recognition Awards and an honorary degree, recognition of honors graduates and outstanding graduates from each college, and conferring of baccalaureate and graduate degrees.
